# Rental Platform Requirement Document

## 1. Platform Overview
A peer-to-peer rental platform using the Frappe ecosystem for the backend. Users can list props, party supplies, and other inventory for rent. The platform has a South Indian festive theme with rangoli, lotuses, banana leaves, and subtle colors.

## 2. User Roles
- **Site Owner**: Shilpa, who will control most of the listings and day-to-day operations.
- **IT Help/Administrator**: Rajesh, providing technical support and managing the technical setup, but not involved in daily operations.
- **Listers**: Friends or peers who can add their own listings.
- **Renters/Customers**: General users who rent items.


## 3. Item Listings and Add-ons
Users can list props and add-ons (e.g., lights, figurines). Party supplies can also be listed. DIY or how-to videos can be attached to items.
